{
  "stem": "22883.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when Liliana have seen that, she ran right away, and she embarrassed the first-- embarrassed-- embraced the first Russian soldier.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was screaming, you are my liberator, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was when the Russian came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did you then return to Warsaw?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we had to go to another camp because the Russian organized a camp for all foreigners because their policy was to investigate everybody because they thought that they were-- were German collaborators and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they couldn't do it in Vienna, so their policy was to gather all the foreigners in Austria and ship them to the country from where they came.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that organizer, they organized first the Yugoslav, from Yugoslavia people, and the next transport from Vienna, from Wiener Neustadt, there were the Polish people going to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, when we came to Warsaw, we came to my parents'.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came to my parents, well, that weekend, my sister was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I didn't stay long because still there was some kind of hostility toward Liliana and me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to Gdansk, to Danzig, because I heard that in Danzig will be a technical-- the technical university would be-- be open, so I went there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to Canada in 1961, February 17th.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had only three jobs because I'm now retired.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My first job, it was only-- I think it was two months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's RCA Limited in Montreal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second job, longer one because it was more than 10 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was Canadian Marconi Company.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the third and last job was Telesat Canada, here in Ottawa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was an electronics engineer and designer and telecommunication specialist.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
